Greetings {bookingDetails::bookingName}!

We are pleased to confirm your booking at the {title}. Please find your reservation details and a few other general instructions below. In case of any query, feel free to write to us at staysia.bookings@gmail.com

General Instructions:

  1) An Invoice of Rs. {price} will be provided to you on check-in.
  2) Please carry an ID Proof for verification at the Front Desk.

COVID-19 Advisory:

  Since these are trying times for all of us, we humbly ask you to follow COVID-19
  safety guidelines during your travel. Please take necessary precautions, while we
  make sure the hotels do the same for you :)
  

  Looking forward to hosting you at such a prime and stylish location!
  

  Regards,
  The Staysia Booking Team
